\f0\fs36 \cf0 # SnapBrand \'97 AI Brand Kit Generator\
\
## What This Is\
AI-powered brand identity generator. User describes their business \uc0\u8594  AI generates a complete brand kit (logo concept, color palette, typography, taglines, brand voice, social templates). Free tier (3 generations) + Pro ($9.99/mo unlimited + high-res downloads).\
\
## Tech Stack\
- **Framework:** Next.js 14 (App Router)\
- **Auth:** Supabase Auth (Google OAuth + email/password)\
- **Database:** Supabase (Postgres + RLS)\
- **Payments:** Stripe (subscription, $9.99/mo Pro plan)\
- **AI:** OpenAI GPT-4o (structured brand data) + DALL-E 3 (logo concepts)\
- **Storage:** Vercel Blob (generated images)\
- **Hosting:** Vercel\
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS\
- **Ads:** Google AdSense slots on SEO pages\
\
## Project Structure\
```\
app/\
  page.tsx                    # Homepage = the generate tool (landing page IS the product)\
  results/[id]/page.tsx       # Shareable brand kit results page\
  brand-kit/[vertical]/page.tsx  # Programmatic SEO pages (30+ verticals)\
  compare/[slug]/page.tsx     # Competitor comparison pages\
  pricing/page.tsx            # Pricing page (Free vs Pro)\
  api/\
    generate/route.ts         # Core AI generation endpoint\
    download/route.ts         # Gated download endpoint (Pro only)\
    webhooks/stripe/route.ts  # Stripe webhook handler\
lib/\
  supabase.ts                 # Supabase client\
  stripe.ts                   # Stripe helpers\
  openai.ts                   # OpenAI client + prompts\
  verticals.ts                # Vertical data for programmatic SEO pages\
  auth.ts                     # Auth helpers\
components/\
  GenerateForm.tsx             # Business input form\
  BrandKitDisplay.tsx          # Renders the full brand kit\
  ColorPalette.tsx             # Color swatch display with copy-on-click\
  TypographyPreview.tsx        # Live Google Fonts preview\
  PricingCard.tsx              # Pricing tier cards\
  AdSlot.tsx                   # Google AdSense wrapper\
  Header.tsx\
  Footer.tsx\
```\
\
## Core User Flow\
1. User lands on homepage \uc0\u8594  sees generate form\
2. Enters: business name, type (dropdown), description, style preference\
3. Optionally uploads a product photo or logo inspiration\
4. Clicks "Generate My Brand Kit"\
5. /api/generate calls GPT-4o for structured JSON + DALL-E 3 for logo image\
6. Results saved to Supabase, images to Vercel Blob\
7. Redirected to /results/[id] \'97 shareable page\
8. Free users: can view everything, downloads are watermarked\
9. Pro users: high-res downloads, PDF export, unlimited generations\
\
## Rate Limiting\
- Anonymous users: 3 generations per browser session (tracked via cookie + Supabase)\
- Authenticated free users: 3 generations total\
- Pro subscribers: unlimited\
\
## Important Rules\
- Homepage IS the product \'97 no separate "app" or "dashboard" page\
- Every /brand-kit/[vertical] page must have unique H1, meta title, meta description\
- Every page must include the generate form (pre-filled with vertical if on vertical page)\
- Results pages must have proper OG meta tags for social sharing\
- Use Google Fonts embed for typography previews (load dynamically based on AI output)\
- Color palette must show hex codes with copy-on-click functionality\
- All Stripe webhooks must verify signatures\
- Supabase RLS must be enabled on all tables\
- AdSense slots: leaderboard (728x90) on vertical pages, rectangle (300x250) on results\
